<br>
Otherwise I want to get the survey out with the very questions we have ALL had.  I want to see how the guilds feel overall.<br>
<br>
And to bitch about the big guilds not having a say -- sigh.  I'd be quite happy to to two totals on the results -- one offering weight based on size of guild -- to see if it has a dramatic difference on the results.  But I am NOT going to try to survey the entire server.  And I don't believe some sort of free-for-all survey is representative, because it's just too darned easy to flood it.  Heck, one dedicated person could completely skew the results.<br>
